# Completion — Never "Done" Before All Gates Pass

**Firma:** HorosCode · **Produkt:** HorosCloud

## Region Is NOT Complete Until ALL Are True

- [ ] Mockup analysis documented (`03-mockup-analysis`)
- [ ] AXAML + ViewModel implemented for **one region only**
- [ ] Isolated Preview running (`06-ui-preview`)
- [ ] Screenshot captured at mockup dimensions
- [ ] Review score **≥ 98 / 100** documented (`07-review-loop`)
- [ ] All diff items from review fixed
- [ ] `dotnet build` passes (`08-testing`)
- [ ] `ReadLints` clean on changed files
- [ ] Tokens only from `docs/design-memory.md`
- [ ] **Human Approval received** (`12-human-approval`)

## Shell / App Is NOT Complete Until

- [ ] Every region individually completed (all gates above)
- [ ] Shell assembly reviewed with same 98 gate
- [ ] Final full-app screenshot vs mockup
- [ ] User approved final assembly

## Never Say "Done" When

- Preview was not run
- Screenshot score is missing or < 98
- Human Approval was not requested or received
- Build or lint fails
- Next region was started without approval
- "Mostly matches" is the best description

## Completion Report Template

```markdown
## Region Complete: Header

- Preview: Views/Previews/HeaderPreview.axaml ✓
- Screenshot: reviews/review-header-v2.png ✓
- Score: 98/100 ✓
- Build: dotnet build OK ✓
- Human Approval: [pending / approved by user]
```

